{"tid":1521810,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發！太古廣場附近有呀叔影人大頭！","createTime":"2019-08-31T10:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T11:18:28.000Z","uid":149420,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0b53e0a1c372919b9c3412569b855fc5f468cfca","tid":1521810,"uid":149420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:55:30.000Z","msg":"大家小心<br />\n我望住佢zoom到近一近影人換裝<br />\n我行埋去望住佢佢即刻扮影街景<br />\n跟左佢一陣跟甩左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家認撚住佢個衰樣！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dEuc37L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdEuc37L.jpg&h=a214d30d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H4wZJ7M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH4wZJ7M.jpg&h=5b0dda33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"295493fe892fb3a41fd50d2cc9712e08e2f55729","tid":1521810,"uid":149420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:55:57.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d533cdf1939ea28168ced20c8ff74d41cd238df6","tid":1521810,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:55:58.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推！"},{"pid":"c4a3d215ce7cbdc95819f2ab4cf2f9ab65f1b21c","tid":1521810,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:56:16.000Z","msg":"地區的兒子需要接送<br />\n<br />\n要拖鞋換 小心螢光鞋底路<br />\n<br />\nGASTBY 冰紙巾好似抹到"},{"pid":"342a1d59852e4f4fb5fc37c446cea7921c7519c9","tid":1521810,"uid":139282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:56:34.000Z","msg":"［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. hot sodium carbonate solution</span><br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾</span><br />\n<br />\n3<span style=\"color: red;\">.化妝水</span>/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢</span><br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal"},{"pid":"05a602c480490cb2ad967858d5fbc6e4d34d0882","tid":1521810,"uid":143827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:56:49.000Z","msg":"手足換裝小心"},{"pid":"9c6567f29291310328bd91f2dee05d2896407be1","tid":1521810,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:56:55.000Z","msg":"又係佢？"},{"pid":"78c9d0cb97f03d2f6bf65db0fddbb6a41c33261c","tid":1521810,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:57:29.000Z","msg":"執粒龍蛋比佢"},{"pid":"ac7c254333441094dc9b2e301a8c4d424b3fbc35","tid":1521810,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:57:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb7603e85e846a2c36d88593c1ec1d5cc1e9c1d","tid":1521810,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:59:30.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"1773d1ba2ff8f39b15394ba745aa6ffe569f7425","tid":1521810,"uid":271644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:02:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03f3eecf4d69e71f553b976d1cd802711a9c5717","tid":1521810,"uid":149420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:17:34.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b6742a66f2547860962f0dd490c08d10b9990b40","tid":1521810,"uid":264051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:18:28.000Z","msg":"搶手機掟撚爆佢算啦"}]}